dc_description_s: 1 map ; 34 x 46 cm.|Relief shown pictorially.|North oriented to right.|Includes decorative title cartouche complete with a coat of arms depicting a city.|Includes illustrations of ships and monster.|This state was published in the Novus Atlas by Jan Jansson in 1680.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
